{
  "texts": [
    "In some contexts, AI may negatively affect both human individuality and group performance (Fügener et al., 2021).",
    "It is therefore important to examine whether the extensive adoption of GenAI may deskill creative workers and affect their ability to produce or evaluate creative outputs, both at an individual and a team level.",
    "Such studies could also examine whether this impact varies depending on the creative task, individual, or team characteristics (e.g., expertise, seniority, team composition, etc.)",
    "and help establish good practices for designing and using GenAI systems that aid rather than hinder human creativity.",
    "A closely related issue is the impact of creativity automation on the nature of creative work, as it may affect aspects of creative roles from which creative professionals draw meaning and satisfaction."
  ]
}